dataLineage.statement:
Layer was to ITOS in an email from UNOCHA, then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following was found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Created and populated Admin0 and 1 name and p-code fields. 2. Created and populated reference name field. 3. P-codes, where applicable, have been restored from previous COD. New p-codes have been constructed for new units. 4. Found and fixed 1 gap error and 1 overlap error. 5. Fixed small nesting errors between layers. 6. Admin2 name "Nioro du rip" was converted to Proper Case.
